dc_title_s: Tenpō kaisei shūchū Kyō ezu Ikeda Tōritei kōsei.
dc_description_s: Mounted cover title. Wood block print. Oriented with north to the left. In Japanese. Relief shown pictorially. Includes legend. 1 map: col.; 32 x 43 cm., folded in cover 16 x 9 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
